-kai-star-ralph-macchio-teases-big-80s-movie-ending-3816939">“它是为了拥抱80年代的大型电影结局。”</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ralph-macchio-wants-cobra-kai-movie-in-two-or-three-years-3837478">拉尔夫·麦基奥（Ralph Macchio）的帖子要“ Cobra Kai”电影《两三年之内》</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
